text: Hurricane Rosa was the only Pacific hurricane to make landfall during the 1994 Pacific hurricane season. It killed at least 4 people in Mexico. Rosa was the 18th named storm and the 10th hurricane of the 1994 Pacific hurricane season. ==Statistics== *Highest Wind Speed: 1 Minute Sustained 100 mph/160 km/h *Pressure: 974mb *Damage: US$700 Million Category:East Pacific hurricanes Category:Hurricanes in Mexico Category:1994 in North America Category:1990s in weather
title: Hurricane Rosa (1994)
